data.description: Beautiful corner lot with extra concrete pad, plenty of room and roof new in 2021! Brand new water treatment system. This 3 bed, 2 bath home is clean and ready to move in, with an open concept, plenty of light, room to run with the big back yard. No carpeting, perfect for a family or someone with a giant trailer for the side pad. You'll love this home! Septic in the front, so free to install a ridiculously big pool in backyard!
